{"type":"text","timestamp":1775847777913,"sessionID":"ses_2873beb82ffetx3oT5NkuHpa9e","part":{"id":"prt_d78c50a2d001VMWZQcgMWQAjgj","messageID":"msg_d78c4f644001xaql7EqrJusoNC","sessionID":"ses_2873beb82ffetx3oT5NkuHpa9e","type":"text","text":"I'll create a comprehensive tasks.md checklist for AR-008, breaking it down into atomic, independently verifiable tasks based on the design document.","time":{"start":1775847777910,"end":1775847777910}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847778040,"sessionID":"ses_2873beb82ffetx3oT5NkuHpa9e","part":{"id":"prt_d78c6a67a001Sk07fF8l1L8Q21","messageID":"msg_d78c4f644001xaql7EqrJusoNC","sessionID":"ses_2873beb82ffetx3oT5NkuHpa9e","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-74436aa5b2ef422eacab5b09bef2254d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制 Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\n**Language**: Go\n**Size**: S\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Create GC package structure and initialize configuration\n- [ ] Verify `pkg/workloadmanager` directory exists\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/` subdirectory\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/config.go`\n  - [ ] Define `GCConfig` struct\n    - [ ] `Interval time.Duration` - GC run interval\n    - [ ] `MaxAge time.Duration` - Maximum age for sandboxes\n    - [ ] `IdleTimeout time.Duration` - Idle timeout for inactive sandboxes\n    - [ ] `DryRun bool` - Dry run mode flag\n    - [ ] `Namespaces []string` - Namespaces to process\n    - [ ] `LabelSelector string` - Label selector filter\n  - [ ] Define `DefaultGCConfig()` function returning default configuration\n    - [ ] Set Interval to 5 * time.Minute\n    - [ ] Set MaxAge to 24 * time.Hour\n    - [ ] Set IdleTimeout to 1 * time.Hour\n    - [ ] Set DryRun to false\n    - [ ] Set Namespaces to empty slice (all namespaces)\n    - [ ] Set LabelSelector to empty string\n- [ ] Create unit tests in `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/config_test.go`\n  - [ ] Test DefaultGCConfig returns expected defaults\n  - [ ] Test GCConfig field types\n- [ ] Verify package compiles: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/gc/...`\n\n**Verification**: Run `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/gc/...` to ensure package structure compiles\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: Implement GC policy engine\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/policy.go`\n- [ ] Define `GCPolicy` struct\n  - [ ] `MaxAgeThreshold time.Duration` - Maximum age threshold\n  - [ ] `IdleThreshold time.Duration` - Idle activity threshold\n  - [ ] `OrphanPolicy OrphanPolicy` - Orphan handling policy\n- [ ] Define `OrphanPolicy` type as string\n- [ ] Define OrphanPolicy constants\n  - [ ] `OrphanPolicyDelete = \"delete\"`\n  - [ ] `OrphanPolicyKeep = \"keep\"`\n  - [ ] `OrphanPolicyReconcile = \"reconcile\"`\n- [ ] Implement `NewGCPolicy(config *GCConfig) *GCPolicy`\n  - [ ] Initialize policy with config values\n  - [ ] Set default OrphanPolicy to OrphanPolicyDelete\n- [ ] Implement `ShouldGC(sandbox *unstructured.Unstructured, sessionInfo *SessionInfo) bool`\n  - [ ] Return true if sandbox meets any GC criteria\n  - [ ] Check IsExpired\n  - [ ] Check IsIdle\n  - [ ] Check IsOrphaned\n- [ ] Implement `IsExpired(sandbox *unstructured.Unstructured) bool`\n  - [ ] Get creation timestamp from metadata\n  - [ ] Compare with MaxAgeThreshold\n  - [ ] Return true if older than threshold\n- [ ] Implement `IsIdle(sandbox *unstructured.Unstructured, sessionInfo *SessionInfo) bool`\n  - [ ] Get last activity time from session info\n  - [ ] Compare with IdleThreshold\n  - [ ] Return true if idle longer than threshold\n- [ ] Implement `IsOrphaned(sandbox *unstructured.Unstructured, sessionInfo *SessionInfo) bool`\n  - [ ] Check if sessionInfo is nil\n  - [ ] Check if sessionInfo.SessionID is empty\n  - [ ] Return true if sandbox has no associated session\n- [ ] Create unit tests in `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/policy_test.go`\n  - [ ] Test NewGCPolicy initialization\n  - [ ] Test ShouldGC with expired sandbox\n  - [ ] Test ShouldGC with idle sandbox\n  - [ ] Test ShouldGC with orphaned sandbox\n  - [ ] Test ShouldGC with active sandbox (should return false)\n  - [ ] Test IsExpired with various ages\n  - [ ] Test IsIdle with various idle times\n  - [ ] Test IsOrphaned with and without session\n  - [ ] Test OrphanPolicy constants\n\n**Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/gc -run TestGCPolicy` to verify policy tests pass\n\n---\n\n#